.TH TRANSCRIBE-CLIENT 1 "February 2025" "parakeet-transcribe 0.3.2" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
transcribe-client \- client for transcribe-daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B transcribe-client
.RI [ audio.wav ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B transcribe-client
sends audio to
.BR transcribe-daemon (1)
for fast transcription.
.PP
Without arguments, records from the microphone for 5 seconds
(configurable via TRANSCRIBE_DURATION environment variable).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.I audio.wav
Path to audio file (optional). If not provided, records from microphone.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B TRANSCRIBE_DURATION
Recording duration in seconds (default: 5)
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Transcribe a file:
.B transcribe-client recording.wav
.TP
Record and transcribe:
.B transcribe-client
.TP
Record for 10 seconds:
.B TRANSCRIBE_DURATION=10 transcribe-client
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR transcribe-daemon (1),
.BR dictee (1)
.SH AUTHOR
rcspam <rcspams@gmail.com>
